snippet: Gov. Sean Parnell said Thursday that he had requested and received the resignation of Thomas Katkus, the adjutant general of the Alaska National Guard.
abstract: Alaska Gov Sean Parnell, upon request, receives resignation of adjutant general of Alaska National Guard Thomas Katkus; request by governor came after report into allegations of sexual assault in Guard found that victims do not trust system due to lack of confidence in the command.
lead_paragraph: Gov. Sean Parnell said Thursday that he had requested and received the resignation of Thomas Katkus, the adjutant general of the Alaska National Guard.
